30
00:03:24,025 --> 00:03:25,160
Eri!

31
00:03:27,507 --> 00:03:29,867
Kenapa kau berisik sekali?

32
00:03:30,737 --> 00:03:34,277
Kenapa? Kau baru dioperasi.

33
00:03:34,637 --> 00:03:36,607
Itu hanya operasi usus buntu.

